<blog>
# Anki 

## 1. 

Anki  Rust  Python  Qt  TypeScript  Web  AGPL-3.0-or-later 

WindowsmacOSLinuxAnki 

## 2. 

### 

Anki 

- **Rust  (rslib)**
- **Python  (pylib/rsbridge)** PyO3  Rust  Python
- **Python  (pylib/anki)** API
- **Qt  (qt/aqt)** PyQt 
- **TypeScript  (ts)** Svelte  Web 

### 



```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Qt] --> B[Python]
    B --> C[Rust]
    C --> D[(SQLite)]
    E[TypeScript] --> B
    F[] --> C
```

### 



```mermaid
graph LR
    Qt[Qt] --> Python[Python]
    Python --> Rust[Rust]
    Rust --> SQLite[(SQLite)]
    Web[TypeScript] --> Python
    Rust --> Sync[]
    Python --> Media[]
```

### 



```mermaid
flowchart TD
    User[] --> Interface[]
    Interface --> Controller[]
    Controller --> Service[]
    Service --> Core[Rust]
    Core --> Storage[]
    Storage --> Core
    Core --> Service
    Service --> Interface
    Interface --> User
```

```rust
fn runtime_handle(&self) -> runtime::Handle {
    self.runtime
        .get_or_init(|| {
            runtime::Builder::new_multi_thread()
                .worker_threads(1)
                .enable_all()
                .build()
                .unwrap()
        })
        .handle()
        .clone()
}
```
